# SignalR-Async

<p align="center">
<a href="https://app.travis-ci.com/sam-mosleh/signalr-async" target="_blank">
    <img src="https://app.travis-ci.com/sam-mosleh/signalr-async.svg?branch=master" alt="Test">
</a>

